<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cancellation Confirmation - Patient</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #6b7280;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .doctor-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3::before {
            content: "üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .cancellation-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .details-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .details-title::before {
            content: "üìã";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .appointment-id {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .appointment-id strong {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .next-steps ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Cancellation Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">‚úÖ Cancellation Confirmed</div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{cancelerName}},</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Your appointment cancellation has been confirmed successfully. We've processed your 
                request and updated our records accordingly.
            </div>
            
            <div class="doctor-info">
                <h3>Doctor Information</h3>
                <div class="doctor-name">{{otherPartyName}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cancellation-details">
                <div class="details-title">Canceled Appointment Details</div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Appointment ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#{{appointmentId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What You Can Do Next:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Book a new appointment anytime through our platform</li>
                    <li>Browse available doctors and time slots</li>
                    <li>Contact our support team if you need assistance</li>
                    <li>Check your appointment history in your dashboard</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-id">
                <strong>Appointment ID:</strong> #{{appointmentId}}
            </div>
            
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Book New Appointment</a>
            
            <div class="message">
                Thank you for using SID Clinic. We hope to see you again soon for your healthcare needs.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing SID Clinic for your healthcare needs.</p>
            <p class="contact-info">Need help? Contact us at support@sidclinic.com</p>
            <p>¬© 2024 SID Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
